{"tid":1752634,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[風向製造所] 乘勝追擊 如何引導藍絲風向","createTime":"2019-11-24T22:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:12:44.000Z","uid":126889,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca18d761a38856edd876b85169c3ec04553089a","tid":1752634,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:29:59.000Z","msg":"大夢初醒型: 原來我地先係少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解架 點解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n憤世型: 政府點解咁都搞唔掂止暴制亂!點解可以咁垃圾! 我以後都唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放手型: 唉! 不如都比下後生話事 可能我地真係老左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好攬炒型: 再咁落去唔係辦法 點解政府仲唔讓步 林鄭搞唔掂就唔好撐到咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懶醒分析型: 其實除左出黎果班後生仔 仲有好多沉默又沉默既大大多數一路睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊邊岩邊邊錯大家有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n失敗主義型: 香港比D暴徒玩完啦 冇啦我地又老個頭近 點都唔夠後生長命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有險可守型: 仲有立法會未輸 我地仲未輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 區議會我地藍絲都未算輸哂<br />\n<br />\n老鼠成型: 其實後生仔要民主諗深一層都不無道理 係止暴制亂途中要聽埋越黎越大既民主訴求先係正路<br />\n<br />\n悲天憫人型: 點解香港變成咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我熟悉的香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfb7a2412520e9f55000b1eafb9ae02c5c2afde","tid":1752634,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推一野"},{"pid":"faa727fb90b40d682db9ef4eab6ff7ec7680598d","tid":1752634,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:32:45.000Z","msg":"岩呀 比佢地受下就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc85e19b1482228e8ec74ae0798e5a43e95d37cc","tid":1752634,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:33:29.000Z","msg":"推策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5f2c9adc20c17e921d1fdae1517ae41fd91e87","tid":1752634,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:36:59.000Z","msg":"寓恥笑於吹風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8ff4f1e0c91ae6cac152fd5b83604716ccee91","tid":1752634,"uid":279840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:38:36.000Z","msg":"要做， 大做， 即刻做"},{"pid":"3440f6628dbf39064c8d3b87ea4385cffe4c99cb","tid":1752634,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8becad379c9908796276c6ad85459e3867212cc2","tid":1752634,"uid":126889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor